a.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/STEV/111%2c%e5%ba%97%e5%b0%8f%2c109%2c20220309%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"STEV,111,店小,109,20220309,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"店小","JNO":"109","JDATE":"20220309","JTITLE":"損害賠償"}